rows.label: qst103408_msg0005
rows.name: I hope you don't think this is over.

rows.label: qst103408_msg0006
rows.name:
Brionac is not the only organization
planning rebellion against the
Superbian Empire.

rows.label: qst103408_msg0007
rows.name: I'm afraid there is no time.

rows.label: qst103408_msg0008
rows.name:
In mere moments, I will return
to my Core Crystal.

rows.label: qst103408_msg0009
rows.name:
I will forget everything.
Even the ideals I have long
pursued by his side...

rows.label: qst103408_msg0010
rows.name:
But the things we have accomplished...
I cannot bear for them to be forgotten.

rows.label: qst103408_msg0011
rows.name:
If you are left no alternative, surely you
will seek my people out... That way, our
deeds will live on in your minds...

rows.label: qst103408_msg0013
rows.name:
Remember...that name.
Remember it...till your dying day!
Gahahah...
